The paper deals with information extraction from text using regular expressions and relational algebra, which are commonly studied in the fields of databases (cs.DB) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The complexity analysis and algorithmic techniques used in the paper are related to computational complexity (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
